snippet.title: Tsunami 2265 - Opening
snippet.description:
Tsunami 2265 is a scifi 3rd-Person shooter PC game released in September 2002 by Got Game Entertainment. It features decent 3D Japanese Anime-inspired design and presentation but outweighed by its many flaws especially the gameplay.

Game's Ending Credits here: /watch?v=UCgc9XXL-gw
